Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.94,0:01:29.98,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.15,0:01:39.14,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}You think we're different
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.14,0:01:42.02,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}You think we never feel the way you do
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:44.58,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}We've got scars to prove we're too
