Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:49.04,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}Fueled by emotions that we thought we knew
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:51.59,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}But really had no clue
